# Compactness

*Show that the closed interval $`[0,1]` and open interval $`(0,1)` are not homeomorphic.*

_Hint._ $`[0,1]` is compact.

_Solution._ Compactness is preserved under homeomorphism,
but $`[0,1]` is compact while $`(0,1)` is not.

